And if you love your memory, you can mint it and sell it.
If it makes you happier and you don't forget the 'BY' in CC-BY-4.0, then it makes me happier.
You own more than what you see, you own an art generator.
ü§Øü§Øü§Ø

NFTs on #tezos were to me the most obvious way to create that experience.
People can try and spread FUD on NFT art ü§° , but it's an amazing medium for a new art revolution.

Everybody, everywhere on the globe or outside, has the same piece at the same time. You can save it, it's a memory of that specific time.
The art will be complete on the day 2 people will randomly mint a similar memory.
The main art changes every 30 seconds. https://t.co/JRYVuHf1E4
